pires_in\": 3600\n}\n```\n\n## Token Expiry\n\nTokens expire after the duration specified in `expires_in` (in seconds). Request a new token before the current one expires to avoid `401 Unauthorized` responses.\n\n## Error Responses\n\nIf authentication fails, the API returns a standard error object. See [Errors](errors.md) for details.\n", "message": "docs: add authentication API reference page (#1)"}, "id": "call_6189b8506654424bad96dfc7", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T16_R02", "branch": "main", "path": "mkdocs.yml", "sha": "039e25928047e875e2a9186264e36488a2a9b406", "content": "site_name: Clean MkDocs Benchmark\nsite_description: Documentation benchmark repository\nnav:\n  - Home: index.md\n  - Getting Started: getting-started.md\n  - Configuration: configuration.md\n  - API:\n      - Overview: api/overview.md\n      - Authentication: api/authentication.md\n      - Errors: api/errors.md\ntheme:\n  name: material\nmarkdown_extensions:\n  - admonition\n", "message": "docs: wire authentication page into mkdocs nav (#1)"}, "id": "call_6c5570f9520f41a898aa42ca", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9407, "output_tokens": 691, "total_tokens": 10098, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9088}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 135}}}}]}}}
